query:
INSERT INTO transportation (
  tripId, type, origin, destination, departureDate, arrivalDate,
  confirmationNumber, website, price, currency, paymentStatus, notes,
  company, carModel, pickupLocation, returnLocation, phone, linkedDocumentId,
  createdAt, updatedAt
)
SELECT 
  tripId, 
  'car_rental' as type,
  pickupLocation as origin,
  returnLocation as destination,
  pickupDate as departureDate,
  returnDate as arrivalDate,
  confirmationNumber,
  website,
  price,
  currency,
  paymentStatus,
  notes,
  company,
  carModel,
  pickupLocation,
  returnLocation,
  phone,
  linkedDocumentId,
  createdAt,
  updatedAt
FROM car_rentals;
